  m_text: "About US\n  \nAn indie game crafted by a passionate 3-person team. Built
    with Unity, this game brings together creativity, challenge, and a deep love
    for immersive gameplay. Designed for gamers who appreciate thoughtful design
    and smooth mechanics.\n\n\nDevelopment Team\n  \nStudio Name: EQUINOX INTERACTIVE 
    \nTeam Members:  \nBadutZY\n- Lead Programmer\n- Game Designer\n\nSwimmingFox\n-
    Art Director\n- UI/UX Designer\n\nAri8Bit\n- Sound Designer\n- Project Manager\n\n\nTechnical
    Info\n  \nVersion: Beta 3.5\nPlatform: Windows\nEngine: Unity 2022.2.21\nRealease
    Date: April 2025\n\n\nContact\n\nWebsite: equinox-interactive.vercel.app\nInstagram:
    @equinox.interactive\nTwitter: @EquinoxIntratve\nSteam: -\n\n\n Acknowledgements\n\nThis
    product contains assets from third-party creators licensed under commercial use,
    including audio, fonts, and graphical materials. All external contributors are
    credited with full attribution and used in accordance with their respective licenses.
    \n\n\nLegal\n\n\xA9 2026 EQUINOX INTERACTIVE. All Rights Reserved.\nAll content,
    trademarks, and registered trademarks are property of their respective owners.\nRedistribution
    or reproduction of this software in any form without prior written consent is
    strictly prohibited.\n\n\nMessage from the Developers\n\n\"Our first project
    as a tiny team of three beginner programmer geeks just building cool stuff because
    we love it\""
